<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Supplement Sheriff 2026 – Amazon Compliance Guard</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .banner { background: #c00; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 10px; font-weight: bold; }
        header { background: #111; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .hero { background: #222; color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .hero h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; color: #ffaa00; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .hero p { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .evidence { background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .evidence-header { font-size: 2rem; color: gold; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .comparison { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 30px; justify-content: center; }
        .before, .after { flex: 1 1 300px; background: #1a1a1a; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .before { border-left: 5px solid #c00; }
        .after { border-left: 5px solid #0c0; }
        .audit-engine { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .price-box { background: gold; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 30px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; }
        .price { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        .step { background: white; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; }
        form label { display: block; text-align: left; margin: 15px 0 5px; font-weight: 600; }
        form input, form input[type="file"] { width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 4px; }
        .submit-btn { background: #c00; color: white; border: none; padding: 15px 40px; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 50px; margin-top: 20px; cursor: pointer; }
        .why { padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
        .features { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 30px; justify-content: center; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .feature { flex: 1 1 300px; text-align: left; background: #fafafa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        footer { background: #111; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 30px; }
        footer a { color: gold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="banner">⏰ DEADLINE: March 31, 2026 – don't wait.</div>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">🛡️ SUPPLEMENT SHERIFF 2026</div>
        <div>The Amazon Compliance Guard</div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>🚨 Catch Compliance Errors Before Amazon Does.</h1>
        <h2>Deadline: March 31, 2026</h2>
        <p>Don't risk your top-selling ASINs to bot suppression. Get a professional human audit that protects your revenue.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 20px;">⏱️ Results usually within the hour | ⚖️ FDA Specialists</div>
    </section>

    <section class="evidence">
        <div class="evidence-header">🏆 REAL CASE: The $49 Audit That Saved an ASIN</div>
        <div class="comparison">
            <div class="before">
                <h3>BEFORE (The Error)</h3>
                <ul style="list-style: none;">
                    <li><strong>Ingredient Typo:</strong> "N,N-Dimenthyl Glycine HCL"</li>
                    <li><strong>Illegal Measure:</strong> "3/16 tsp"</li>
                    <li><strong>Risk Level:</strong> 🔴 HIGH</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="after">
                <h3>AFTER (The Remediation)</h3>
                <ul style="list-style: none;">
                    <li><strong>Corrected Name:</strong> "N,N-Dimethylglycine HCL"</li>
                    <li><strong>FDA Measure:</strong> "¼ tsp (approx.)"</li>
                    <li><strong>Status:</strong> ✅ READY TO PRINT</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="audit-engine">
        <h2>⚡ Instant Audit Request</h2>
        <div class="price-box">
            <span class="price">$49.00</span> <span>(One ASIN / One Label)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h3>Step 1: Pay with PayPal</h3>
            <a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_xclick&business=YOUR_PAYPAL_EMAIL&item_name=Supplement+Sheriff+Audit&amount=49.00&currency_code=USD" target="_blank">
                <img src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_paynowCC_LG.gif" alt="Pay Now">
            </a>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">After payment, copy your Transaction ID.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h3>Step 2: Submit Your Details</h3>
            <form action="https://submit-form.com/GOmORATog" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none">
                
                <label>Contact Email:</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Where to send your report">
                
                <label>Product ASIN or Name:</label>
                <input type="text" name="product" required>
                
                <label>Label Upload (Hi-Res):</label>
                <input type="file" name="label" accept="image/*" required>
                
                <label>PayPal Transaction ID:</label>
                <input type="text" name="paypal_txn" required placeholder="17-digit code from PayPal">
                
                <input type="hidden" name="_redirect" value="https://YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME.github.io/supplement-sheriff/thank-you.html">
                
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">SUBMIT FOR ARREST</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="why">
        <h2>🔍 Why Supplement Sheriff?</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>✅ Regulatory Citations</h3>
                <p>We give you exact 21 CFR 101.9 citations for your appeal.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>✅ Math Validation</h3>
                <p>We cross-check every mg, mcg, and serving size.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>✅ Real-Time Monitoring</h3>
                <p>Auditing against March 31, 2026 enforcement patterns.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div>⚖️ 100% Guarantee: If we miss something, we re-audit for free.</div>
        <div style="margin: 10px 0;">Support: <a href="mailto:audit@check-in-sheriff.online">audit@check-in-sheriff.online</a></div>
        <div>© 2026 The Sheriff. Built for Amazon Sellers.</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
